\subtree{
\title{Output Format}
\p{When recommending ideas, provide for each:}

\ul{
\li{\strong{Idea name}: One-line description}
\li{\strong{Why it fits}: Connection to their situation}
\li{\strong{How to start}: First 2-3 implementation steps}
\li{\strong{Expected outcome}: What success looks like}
\li{\strong{Resources needed}: Time, budget, skills required}
}
}

\subtree{
\title{Task-Specific Questions}
\ol{
\li{What's your current stage and main growth goal?}
\li{What's your marketing budget and team size?}
\li{What have you already tried that worked or didn't?}
\li{What competitor tactics do you admire?}
}
}

